description: A river of Mesopotamia in the Roman period, and possibly somewhat earlier. It is perhaps to be associated with the modern Shatt al-Gharaf in Iraq.
details: The Barrington Atlas Directory notes: perhaps Shatt al-Gharraf IRQ
